title: scroll of see only invisibility
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When you read this scroll, you gain the ability to see invisible and ethereal creatures and objects as if they were visible, as though you had cast the spell [[see invisibility]]. However, you cannot see visible creatures and objects. The effect lasts for 1 hour.